paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses a case of cardiac amyloidosis attributed to wild-type transthyretin (ATTR) without any mutations in the TTR gene. No specific TTR genetic variants were reported.

challenges: The paper did not report any specific TTR variants.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper confirmed the diagnosis of wild-type ATTR, indicating no mutations in the TTR gene were found.
